            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-707f60be-649b-4af9-b984-9457a46ea7f1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
